  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "アニメ「おじゃる丸」の世界が舞台です。サイコロを振って町を移動し、ミニゲームをプレイしてポイントを増やし、ゴールを目指しましょう。対戦プレイも可能です。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "A game of the popular NHK educational anime \"Ojarumaru\". There are 3 modes: \"Tabi-dachi niru (single-player mode)\", \"Tokukun-itashimasu (mini-game mode)\", and \"Welcome to me (two-player battle mode)\". Set in Moonlight Town, the game is played in a sugoroku format, collecting items placed in each square, playing against each other in a mini game, and more when one of them finishes at the pond. The one who collects the points of is the winner.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
